    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Glyceryl PPG-16/SMDI HEA/Hydroxyisopropyl Methacrylate is made by reacting PPG-16 Glyceryl Ether with an excess of saturated methylene diphenyldiisocyanate (SMDI). The unreacted isocyanate from the first reaction is then reacted with a mixture of hydroxyethylacrylate (HEA) and hydroxyisopropyl methacrylic acid."
